<chapter xml:id="chapter-1" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Introduction to the Textbook</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      Welcome to our textbook!
      This textbook was written to support you in learning foundational knowledge about Earth's atmosphere to better understand our weather and climate.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before diving into the study of Earth's weather and climate,
      we will introduce several fundamental terms and concepts that will be used throughout this textbook,
      starting with the most crucial: an atmosphere.
    </p>
  </introduction>

